Guest houses

Guest houses

   [logissaintaubinexterieur.jpg?itok=093kJoMc]

See our list of guest houses

   Looking for a guest house in Angers? A place where you can set down
   your bags and take things slow?

   Staying in the home of a local, enjoying cooking secrets shared by your
   host and tasting regional produce are all part of the charm of staying
   in a guest house in Angers. Sit back and enjoy the authenticity,
   refinement and friendly welcome provided by local guest house owners.
   Book your stay in a guest house with one click!
